{"tid":95942,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[推到完場] 港台33 - 世情 2 - 貓島之人生 (21:00)","createTime":"2017-01-26T12:06:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T14:06:23.000Z","uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"60ebe9becf8c3bb4d14c51252740b2fcd3595da1","tid":95942,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T12:06:30.000Z","msg":"貓島之人生<br />\n<br />\n日本田代島住了過百隻貓，被稱為「貓島」。隨着年輕一輩遷走，老人家一個個過身，這個寧靜小島逐漸衰落，現時全島只剩下五、六十個老人家與貓為伴。但島上人的鄰里關係十分好，一方有難，八方支援。<br />\n<br />\n島民與貓的感情深厚，幾乎每隻貓都有名字。以前，田代島有很多農家，依靠種田維生，但老鼠出沒吃掉不少稻米和小麥，於是家家戶刀開始養貓治鼠。島上甚至興建貓神社，奉貓為神明。島上每戶人都有自己與貓的獨特故事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://programme.rthk.hk/assets/images/rthk/dtt31/differentlives2/originals/mfile_7471_412336_6_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fprogramme.rthk.hk%2Fassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fdifferentlives2%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_7471_412336_6_l.jpg&h=85c1c741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"http://programme.rthk.hk/assets/images/rthk/dtt31/differentlives2/originals/mfile_7471_412336_1_l.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fprogramme.rthk.hk%2Fassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fdifferentlives2%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_7471_412336_1_l.jpg&d=K43woMbQiM9c16wEEDxDM3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=869dd66b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://programme.rthk.hk/assets/images/rthk/dtt31/differentlives2/originals/mfile_7471_412336_1_l.jpg</a><br />\n[/img]"},{"pid":"648c0a67413e5cbab7c9562972184dca03f6e925","tid":95942,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T12:07:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://programme.rthk.hk/assets/images/rthk/dtt31/differentlives2/originals/mfile_7471_412336_1_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fprogramme.rthk.hk%2Fassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fdifferentlives2%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_7471_412336_1_l.jpg&h=671ddc38&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8eaa9ced19e06d963f9b9d40f12306f8f778b90b","tid":95942,"uid":51